      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "Hi.\nWe are running the pre-checks for our design and we are getting no DRC violations but some antenna errors. \nLooking at the report all of them are related to the via1(area)/poly gate(area)  ratio.\nHave anyone got something similar? Could explaing a little bit more about the error and how to fix it?\nAny feedback would be appreciated.\nThanks,\nLuighi",
