      "timestampEdited": null,
      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "Hi! This error could appear if you have too much VIAs on a single layer on a wire connected to a gate. See rules here: https://gf180mcu-pdk.readthedocs.io/en/latest/physical_verification/design_manual/drm_08.html . If you select a single violation in lyrdb you could see which gate has violations and the values of calculated antenna parameters for this gate for the violated check.",
